Yeah but this is about as blunt as a mace blow to the face. Alundra was called 'Alundra' because the iconic character of the game was ALUNDRA, the Zelda Series at least always had a Zelda, final fantasy.. I don't know how to start on that really, considering the first game was called Final Fantasy it amuses me that there's been so many 'Final' fantasy games *snort* humorous at best.

But Alundra 2 didnt feature "Alundra" at all, no mention, no references, no dreamwalking. Nada.
